is a labour of love, motivated by a desire to help everyone live in greener and healthier spaces. Our core purpose is to profit share in order to raise money for the Rainforest Alliance. We have chosen this organisation due to its combined focus on ecological preservation and the rights of indigenous peoples, a focus which mirrors our own ethical concerns. It is this combination of core principles that has motivated us to focus our profit sharing initiatives with this group. We do however have other, more local profit-sharing dreams afoot, and as we grow, we would welcome discussions about worthy partners in this.
